44:["$","p",null,{"children":"差距相當大。npm 有 package provenance、2FA 要求、自動 CVE 掃描等機制。ClawHub 嘅安全審查機制相對新，仍然係由社區自律為主。呢個係點解自己做 5 步審查係必要嘅——唔可以完全依賴平台嘅審查。"}]
45:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：Skill 更新有冇安全風險？"}]}]
46:["$","p",null,{"children":["有。一個原本安全嘅 Skill，作者可以喺更新版本加入惡意代碼。建議 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"skills.auto_update false"}],"，每次更新前手動 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"openclaw skill inspect"}]," 確認新版本冇問題。"]}]
